Smile!  Live, Laugh and Love with this beautiful design. Brighten up your day with this colorful and reversible mat.  Can be used on a table, countertop or hung on a wall.  Stunning eye catcher. Pamper that cat or dog with their own place mat or add to the beauty of that plant you have sitting there. Have a hot dish or a hot pan to set down?  This pretty mat gives you the perfect resting spot.  How about that candle just sitting there? Put it on this mat to add beauty to the flame.

- Approximately 15" x 15" padded mat
- use on table under hot dishes, under a candle, under a plant, etc. or just as table decor
- use as mat for under cat or dog food dishes
- washable (may soften some with washing)
- reversible
- mat features live, laugh, love, family print fabric
